1. Dobrodošla si u našu kuću! (Welcome to our house!)
2. Drago mi je da si dobrodošla u našu kancelariju. (I'm glad you're welcome in our office.)
3. Dobrodošla u naš tim! (Welcome to our team!)
4. Hvala ti na dobrodošlici! (Thank you for the welcome!)
5. Dobrodošla, kako si provela vikend? (Welcome, how was your weekend?)
6. Bila sam jako umorna, ali dobrodošla je bila promena okoline. (I was very tired, but the change of scenery was welcome.)
7. Javila mi se stara prijateljica koju nisam videla godinama. Dobrodošla iznenadjenja! (An old friend who I haven't seen in years called me. Welcome surprise!)
8. Dobrodošla novim izazovima! (Welcome to new challenges!)
9. Znam da si nova u gradu, ali želim ti dobrodošlu dobrodošlicu! (I know you're new to town, but I want to give you a warm welcome!)
10. Dobrodošla sam, ali još uvek nisam pronašla svoje mesto. (I am welcome, but I have not yet found my place.)